      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YOU AIN'T IT (2) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish third, beaten 5.5 lengths (19.65) at Angle Park in a Best 8 over 342m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. One of the contenders. CARRY ON NATASHA (3) has a strong record this track and trip with five wins and three placings from 10 starts. Recorded a one length win (19.46) in a Grade 4/5 last time at Angle Park. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. SPONSORSHIP (6) lines up chasing another win after getting around the 375m at Broken Hill in a handy 21.91 two back then following up with a 22.51 win at this track over 400m last time. Flying lately and can measure up again. VELARIS (8) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
